item.title: Silento - Watch Me
item.description:
For educational use.
Silentó singing Watch Me (Whip/Nae Nae), with the pitch lowered 3 half steps so diatonic color coded handbells can play along.
If you found this video useful please subscribe and share with your friends. If you want to be notified of future videos please click on bell next to subscribe.
[Kristal Bells / Desk Bells / colour hand-bells / seniors / childrens / colored bells]
